{
  "id": "RAW_a72aa922",
  "title": "AI 能不能少点废话，多干点活？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247536669&idx=1&sn=b9da01973eaee6c3b82a012f1f35e5b9",
  "date": "2026-01-22 12:20:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8503b616&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3TicKSqH32P1Vub0bdMjQibuaUAXMERdOPTRMiatBUTnccRXIdQhbpU5tkiaQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两年，AI 在写代码这件事上的进步，说实话有点不讲道理。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不管是 MiniMax、Claude 这些大模型，还是 Cursor、Claude Code 这种编程工具，现在写代码基本已经进入了「动动嘴」阶段。很多时候，你只需要把需求说清楚，剩下的交给它就行。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但只要你把视角从“写代码”稍微挪开一点，现实立刻就变了。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理文件、筛选信息、跑流程、处理各种零碎事务——这些才是大多数工作里最耗时、最磨人，但又最难被自动化的部分。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 工具其实已经很多了，但用下来会发现一个很明显的共性：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">它们大多停留在“给建议”这一步。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你问它怎么做，它会告诉你思路；</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">你让它总结，它能写得头头是道；</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可一旦涉及「真正动手」，比如进文件夹、操作网页、跑一整套流程，它往往就卡住了。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近在整理一些非代码工作的过程中，正好看到 MiniMax Agent</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;更新上线。它宣传的点并不是模型升级，而是开始让 AI 去“干活”。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚好我自己一直在订阅 MiniMax 的 Coding Plan（也是目前唯一订阅的国产大模型），就顺手试了一下，看看模型之外，它的 Agent 能力到底靠不靠谱。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI Native Workspace：从聊天室到工作台</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniMax Agent 这次的思路，其实挺克制的。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它没有试图再造一个更聪明的聊天框，而是把重点放在了两个非常具体的能力上：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Desktop</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：让 Agent 能操作本地文件和网页环境</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Expert Agents</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：围绕具体任务封装能力，而不是泛泛对话</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">背后的判断其实很清楚：现在真正限制 AI 落地的，已经不是“会不会想”，而是“能不能做”。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多非代码工作的问题，并不是模型不会推理，而是它根本进不来你的真实环境——看不到你的文件结构，碰不到你的素材，点不了你的网页。</span></p>\n      <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniMax Agent 想做的，就是把这道墙拆掉一部分。</span></p>\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top: 16px;padding: 0.5em 1em 0.5em 12px;font-size: 1.2em;border-radius: 6px;line-height: 1.6;border-left: 4px solid #1677ff;border-right: 1px solid rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.1);border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.1);border-top: 1px solid rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.1);background: rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.05);color: #1677ff;margin: 2em 0 0.75em;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何使用？</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Desktop 安装包可以直接在 MiniMax Agent 官网下载：</span></p>\n      <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 16px;font-style: italic;margin: 20px 0;padding: 12px 20px;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.04);border-left: 4px solid #0066ff;border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0;color: #4e5969;\"><span leaf=\"\">下载地址：<a href=\"https://agent.minimaxi.com/download\" target=\"_blank\">https://agent.minimaxi.com/download</a></span></p>\n      </blockquote>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5231481481481481\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052992\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f336235&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3TiciaGLdC1ibyhM2fdSiaHBBic1jJAKouFxBJZQZx2Dc04M4ibyV6U6lvKlpNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Expert Agents 可以在网页端直接体验：</span></p>\n      <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 16px;font-style: italic;margin: 20px 0;padding: 12px 20px;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.04);border-left: 4px solid #0066ff;border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0;color: #4e5969;\"><span leaf=\"\">在线体验：<a href=\"https://agent.minimaxi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://agent.minimaxi.com/</a></span></p>\n      </blockquote>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5509259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052991\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c34f24d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3TicOR1nzRKHkibiaqQo1SaM02O7ANR1O0ibb7VGjLNfrndqaEYckWHnWaXfA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来我没有做参数对比，也没有跑 Benchmark，而是选了两个非常琐碎、但极其真实的非代码场景，看看它到底能不能顶得上来。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Case 1：治愈我的「后期强迫症」</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一个测试，我没一上来就搞复杂场景，先从一个很常见的问题开始。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近在做一系列 Vibe Coding 项目，项目目录已经被折腾得不成样子。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 生成的文档、脚本、说明文件，经常被随手丢到不太对的地方。README、配置文件、临时脚本、素材混在一起，隔一段时间再回来看，自己都要重新捋一遍。</span></p>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3583333333333334\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052990\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d65018eb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3Tic6UkDNM5OiaEKc79hXaYdp16gCicQtG1VYjr6K4icMPxc3J5kxUvGDmcPg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我直接把整个项目目录交给 MiniMax Agent，让它做三件事：</span></p>\n      <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 16px;font-style: italic;margin: 20px 0;padding: 12px 20px;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.04);border-left: 4px solid #0066ff;border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0;color: #4e5969;\"><span leaf=\"\">识别每个目录/文件大概在干什么、对文件进行分类，给我一个更合理的整理方案。</span></p>\n      </blockquote>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052994\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20bf7736&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3TicARpuGW4e1odiaEadLoq29yObt3poiaiaVeicunL4Fp4lRVxBlW8Afjrdfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <span leaf=\"\">它没有直接乱动文件，而是先给出了一份整理后的结构说明，把核心项目、参考项目、素材、文档、测试代码分得很清楚。</span>\n      <p></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我简单对比了一下，和实际情况基本一致。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时它还给了我两个整理方案（视频里有）：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个是</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">按业务重新分类</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个是</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">尽量少改动现有结构</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我选了第一个，难度更高，但长期更舒服。</span></p>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6324074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052993\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74795aa6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3Tic2tU1IZcIlQlmdVCPy8Uk9b7xMflX0Ij1YGrgLRZcRTp4TERRpgOZag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <span leaf=\"\">说实话，在点确认之前我还有点慌——这个目录里差不多有&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">20 万个文件</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，真怕它给我整乱了。</span>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果证明我多虑了。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它严格按方案执行，把整个目录重新整理了一遍，过程很克制，逻辑也很清楚。</span></p>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30277777777777776\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052995\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c8911f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3TicfRVgnQnNiaohIOhjhZfndUebNnlFYiaq1rDf6huNnjcL2DLOGWB9YiajA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理完成后，还生成了一个可视化页面，用来对比整理前后发生了什么变化：哪些文件被移动了、为什么这么动，全都写清楚了。</span></p>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.4702842377260983\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"774\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052998\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17d9469e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMPcICxwcv6fynA708icsc3Tic0HfpQl9icOPxalV878tjfwdJHIIRPN7Nz2NibXz9ODoCANqkWkWmS2Zg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个场景算是个开胃菜，不复杂，但非常实用。</span></p>\n      <h3 style=\"margin-top: 16px;padding: 0.5em 1em 0.5em 12px;font-size: 1.2em;border-radius: 6px;line-height: 1.6;border-left: 4px solid #1677ff;border-right: 1px solid rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.1);border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.1);border-top: 1px solid rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.1);background: rgba(22, 119, 255, 0.05);color: #1677ff;margin: 2em 0 0.75em;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">难度升级：50G 照片整理</span></h3>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个基础上，我给它上了点难度。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我有一个接近&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">50G</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的照片文件夹，将近&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">3000 张相机原图</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.938375350140056\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"714\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto 0px;display: block;width: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100052996\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91d57b0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO5